Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:06.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水惠 小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:14.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:16.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到就答應一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:21.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛し…愛し合うのさ もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛…更加地相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:02.44,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激しい渇きに狂いそう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:02.44,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激烈的飢渴讓我發狂
