Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:11.63,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}閉上眼睛 罪孽深重的接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:22.39,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}お前の匂い 狂わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:22.39,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的味道 令人發狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:26.35,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真夜中に目覚めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:26.35,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在半夜裡睜開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:29.38,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}狂気 愛 飲み干す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:29.38,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}把愛與瘋狂喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.73,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.73,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}過來 到我的懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.85,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.85,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那邊的黑暗是苦澀的」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:41.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の惑い 揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:41.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你在迷惘 在動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:45.39,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて永遠になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:45.39,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}最終將永遠無法解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.75,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「こっちの闇は甘いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.75,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「這邊的黑暗是甘甜的」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.77,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕は深く 突き刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.77,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我狠狠地刺進最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:57.83,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
